snippet.title: 「4.5th PV」 Piano (KR Ver) / Blue Archive New Login OST "Theme 154"/ 2nd Anniversary
snippet.description:
Blue Archive - 4.5th PV「New Login」 OST "Theme 154" Piano Performance (2nd Anniversary)


There was a broadcast today commemorating the 2nd anniversary of Blue Archive’s Korean and global service launch.
Along with various news, a PV teasing the first episode that will follow the final chapter was also released.

When the Korean version of the 4th PV was released last time, Korean dubbing was added.
This time too, it was replaced with a Korean voice.

'Fox Platoon', which has not appeared as a leading role for a long time,
It seems that the story of 'Kuzunoha' will unfold.

This work was also made with a drawing and feeling similar to the 4th PV,
The illustrations and music are great.
The only regret is that it is so short.

In order to give the feeling that the intro narration part continues from the 4th PV
"RE Aoharu" I composed an intro using the narration part.

The main section of the melody develops with a very fast beat,
A sense of speed and coolness was added through ad-libbing in the treble.

Thank you for listening.
---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
---------------------------------------------------
Blue Archive Main Title OST 「Constant Moderato」 Piano Play : https://youtu.be/qOGJzArDknQ
Blue Archive Memorial BGM 「Midnight Trip」 Piano Play : https://youtu.be/VLaDJCDIA8Q
Blue Archive 1st Anniversary PV OST(Luminous Memory) Piano Play : https://youtu.be/1xhW91bbFS8
[1st Anniversary] Blue Archive 「Target For Love」 Piano & Guitar Ver. : https://youtu.be/fC7HWUYQLdQ
---------------------------------------------------
템플릿 : 론박자막연구소
---------------------------------------------------
